      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;Consider divine resurrection as well. 5aa every 24hrs will give 100% mana. and yes you can use it after you been rezzed, just loot your gear first, then pop it.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Nearing 10k mana myself, I find mana regen to be just fine after a wipe. Yes it takes&amp;nbsp;a few minutes, but the clerics are rezzed first (if raid), if only to get their clicky out and start rezzing others.&amp;nbsp; If I was fm 5min after I buffed after a wipe, the guild wouldnt be. They rethink strats etc.&amp;nbsp; 10 to 15min after clerics are rezzed back into a raid wipe zone, we're back in action.&amp;nbsp; Nothing wrong, move along.&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
