&lt;P&gt;The problem I have with using that ability after a raid wipe is that you are going to have to wait for the rest of the raid to med anyway, so there is little point in div rezzing yourself IMO.&amp;nbsp; I usually save div rez for when I die in the middle of an event and I need to get back into healing ASAP, so I get rezzed, I loot then I div rez myself.&lt;/P&gt;</description>
